/***********************************
*  	     EXECUTION 		   *
***********************************/

Get libuminati project compiled
Get LIBAMA part of libama project compiled ("make libama" in libama/)

/***********************************
*  	     EXECUTION 		   *
***********************************/

1. In a first terminal, launch "./snake". It can be launched from any repository.
2.a. In a second terminal, use "pgrep snake" to find the pid of the program.
2.b. Change ptrace permissions : "echo 0 > /proc/sys/kernel/yama/ptrace_scope" (might need to be done as root)
2.c. Launch manager ("./manager pid").
3.a. In a third terminal, use "pgrep manager" to find the pid of the manager.
3.b. Use "kill -SIGUSR1 managerpid" to start the update.

Notes:
Don't forget to put again a file in dynamic_updates/ before launching an update.

Changes:
Before: taking fruit implies score +50 and increasing speed.
After: taking fruit implies score -5 and decreasing speed.

